data.description: This ranch style home welcomes you first with a circle drive and a large covered front porch. Single story 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home featuring an in home theater, inground pool and large private backyard patio. Master bedroom has a sitting room, large walk in closet and a private master bath with a sunk in tub, separate shower along with dual sinks. Half hall bathroom, formal dining, vaulted ceiling in living room with fireplace and eat in kitchen with flex space. Entertainer's dream backyard, inground pool, large patio and a firepit. Former garage space was professionally converted to an in home theater, with indoor utility and storage room. Roof is was new in 2019, fresh paint inside, and ready for new owners!
